items.sentence: Do you have something you want to say to me?

I heard that Tom can\'t speak French at all.
I hope my last mail didn\'t sound too harsh.
You know that I like to do that, don\'t you?
Tom wanted to ask questions, but he didn\'t.
Another store will be opened in Boston soon.
Anything seemed possible back in those days.
Anything you say to me will be kept private.

I don\'t care about what other people think.
